/>\n我都試下<br />\n<br />\n跑過北韓半馬 你問我答<br />\n5k sub 20 你問我答<br />\n10k sub40 你問我答<br />\n半馬 sub1:40 你問我答"},{"pid":"310688a074ac1d63e1e3e078ab707eadb70ad8bd","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣練心肺架？跑嚟跑去都好慢同跑唔到好長</blockquote><br />\n我由上年8月開始做運動<br />\n一開始都無練跑<br />\n係會所踩左2 3個月單車<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係要踩得耐練好條氣 踩幾慢都好唔好停就得</span><br />\n每次踩個幾鐘<br />\n直到12月先開始練跑<br />\n屋企搵好條岩自己既路線 ie來回3km/5km/7km咁<br />\n之後都係幾慢都好跑到自己既target先好停<br />\n當然你條氣唔順緊係記得停<br />\n但唔好行足全程"},{"pid":"3245daadfb06434d7ac9ed542c1a149793c85db1","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>農曆新年都現在100km<br />\n停左兩個月<br />\n對我來講，要持之以恆，一日跑半粒鐘五公里算<br />\n我跑得太長太耐會覺得辛苦就放棄<br />\n以前會跑到累先停<br />\n近排限住自己停，不過近三日開始跑返</blockquote><br />\n每日5km keep到都好夠運動量"},{"pid":"82553d8a50d7f24e84a8f3b52bb4f7ea1af8e0b4","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打係減肥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當初係失戀做運動麻醉自己<br />\n減肥係其中一個因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6821d3cb646892503f2780c86947e76be0fa904c","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會好悶咩</blockquote><br />\n會架<br />\n所以我唔可以會所同運動場跑<br />\n一定要跑街同聽住歌跑"},{"pid":"da8a955a4e924270d3f82c6de941c3c9d77aeb9a","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打跑開步？ 十公里四分幾五分1k 幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上年11 12月跑到依家<br />\n之前廿幾年都無做過運動<br />\n包括係學校pe堂都全部skip哂"},{"pid":"a1fc7e0cbab16b0d0d4becfa14a17ee93d0a2d82","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>減咗幾多磅</blockquote><br />\n8月135lbs<br />\n10月110lbs<br />\n之後一路keep到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實我係12月先開始跑<br />\n所以都無咩再減落去<br />\n但我係完全暴食mode"},{"pid":"85dd9f0b1148ff2854e98474efab5ab29d6460fe","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:26:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成日跑6k之後跑完腳痛<br />\n所以唔夠膽跑大長<br />\n有冇方法改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSet target到7-8km<br />\n盡量跑埋佢 就算慢啲都好"},{"pid":"35a09c936638499c5c47313fbf9f4b9f3656fae6","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點樣練心肺架？跑嚟跑去都好慢同跑唔到好長</blockquote><br />\n齋跑孚難，要快就交叉訓練</blockquote><br />\n咩叫交叉訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慢跑x快跑</blockquote><br />\n係 我聽過如果要練速度最好係快跑幾分鐘<br />\n停30秒再快跑咁<br />\n不過我無教練亦都無諗過要train自己<br />\n純粹變成興趣"},{"pid":"880aa1665ad367efcf0f7a66e7132597fbcd2f74","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都開到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都試下<br />\n<br />\n跑過北韓半馬 你問我答<br />\n5k sub 20 你問我答<br />\n10k sub40 你問我答<br />\n半馬 sub1:40 你問我答</blockquote><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794828660658045dcde3566f405bdb7aa25fca80","tid":260521,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>減咗幾多磅</blockquote><br />\n8月135lbs<br />\n10月110lbs<br />\n之後一路keep到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實我係12月先開始跑<br />\n所以都無咩再減落去<br />\n但我係完全暴食mode</blockquote><br />\n 巴定絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s