c=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.rice.edu/~jenky/images/itband.2.anat.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rice.edu%2F~jenky%2Fimages%2Fitband.2.anat.gif&h=96218750&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我又唔知喎<br />\n但聽講跑得密好傷腳<br />\n我見無咩事無理到<br />\n亦都好小痛</blockquote><br />\n你踩單車綀左肌力先去跑 應該無事"},{"pid":"958408970970989f50aab3d253d9708f80e550aa","tid":260521,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:00:32.000Z","msg":"已經跑曬呢生人要跑既路<br />\n利申 玩過x country"},{"pid":"cdce3999edb23594d4918477096e288c912eda0d","tid":260521,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:00:37.000Z","msg":"我反而唔係無氣 係腳攰 有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0aed7527ee0e528fe9a32d4920678190f55ca9f","tid":260521,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都開到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都試下<br />\n<br />\n跑過北韓半馬 你問我答<br />\n5k sub 20 你問我答<br />\n10k sub40 你問我答<br />\n半馬 sub1:40 你問我答</blockquote><br />\n人地開post關你撚事咩<br />\n你覺得你10k sub40好快？"},{"pid":"90960d3191698700a52ce5a20bc98c953d1aeccc","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而唔係無氣 係腳攰 有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我既經驗係過左某個range會累<br />\n太快亦都會累<br />\n最緊要搵到個啱自己既路程同速度<br />\n或者好似上面巴打講咁得閒踩車練下都可能有幫助"},{"pid":"cf027ce9c0e52ad2557f0fd124d0d2eeeaef6d41","tid":260521,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T12:12:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我反而唔係無氣 係腳攰 有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我既經驗係過左某個range會累<br />\n太快亦都會累<br />\n最緊要搵到個啱自己既路程同速度<br />\n或者好似上面巴打講咁得閒踩車練下都可能有幫助</blockquote><br />\n果時跟人操講過<br />\nX country 大概頭8分鐘最辛苦"},{"pid":"08c67118fe9a3cf09b988f6fa2768db5dd9c2ed0","tid":260521,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁都開到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都試下<br />\n<br />\n跑過北韓半馬 你問我答<br />\n5k sub 20 你問我答<br />\n10k sub40 你問我答<br />\n半馬 sub1:40 你問我答</blockquote><br />\n人地開post關你撚事咩<br />\n你覺得你10k sub40好快？</blockquote><br />\n味係 死撚開啦 以為自己好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbb8c0d526d88b19816705ec3739da14d8eb0c9","tid":260521,"uid":89928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"你覺得<br />\n1）完全適應晒而家既跑速同距離，先再慢慢增加距離或提升跑速<br />\n2）每一次都選擇一個岩岩好超越自己極限少少既跑速同距離<br />\n<br />\n邊樣好啲？"},{"pid":"8abae0ea397e22465f8cf68f6fda59e3c962242f","tid":260521,"uid":9028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁都開到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都試下<br />\n<br />\n跑過北韓半馬 你問我答<br />\n5k sub 20 你問我答<br />\n10k sub40 你問我答<br />\n半馬 sub1:40 你問我答</blockquote><br />\n人地開post關你撚事咩<br />\n你覺得你10k sub40好快？</blockquote><br />\n味係 死撚開啦 以為自己好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我半馬1:38(唔快）都未出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856e07986960baa5197ccdd570b4d3176fa1812e","tid":260521,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以講下800km具體幾長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1/3個台灣"},{"pid":"ba8ec60ee1632aa2f7c37d245cd161c2e7ff8765","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你覺得<br />\n1）完全適應晒而家既跑速同距離，先再慢慢增加距離或提升跑速<br />\n2）每一次都選擇一個岩岩好超越自己極限少少既跑速同距離<br />\n<br />\n邊樣好啲？</blockquote><br />\n我覺得純興趣/減肥係1好啲<br />\n如果你係要準備比賽無咩時間先會2<br />\n我自己就係1"},{"pid":"cd24e9eae71b0aecd13046ac0e87d3a5a3c8adbc","tid":260521,"uid":89928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T18:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你覺得<br />\n1）完全適應晒而家既跑速同距離，先再慢慢增加距離或提升跑速<br />\n2）每一次都選擇一個岩岩好超越自己極限少少既跑速同距離<br />\n<br />\n邊樣好啲？</blockquote><br />\n我覺得純興趣/減肥係1好啲<br />\n如果你係要準備比賽無咩時間先會2<br />\n我自己就係1</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝謝回答<br />\n我每次跑步跑到1Km已經覺得對腳好攰好想停<br />\n不過死撐一陣之後又跑到6K<br />\n唔知有無問題"},{"pid":"88d963712596a8d77eaa6fd7ca48384dedd4b073","tid":260521,"uid":85046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T19:21:39.000Z","msg":"巴打跑街定跑track?<br />\n<br />\n我成日跑左一次就放棄左<br />\n有冇辦法可以keep到團火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e0d79607ff73e24bb3f336d1d6591f6cc1dfdb","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T01:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打跑街定跑track?<br />\n<br />\n我成日跑左一次就放棄左<br />\n有冇辦法可以keep到團火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑街<br />\n當你成功減到肥唔想再肥返就會有恒心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4ea9ec55a23ec0decbb8f49bf90455ce15681d","tid":260521,"uid":23860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打跑街定跑track?<br />\n<br />\n我成日跑左一次就放棄左<br />\n有冇辦法可以keep到團火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑街<br />\n當你成功減到肥唔想再肥返就會有恒心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未成功之前呢"},{"pid":"398f2225f2be561a425e5aee3eb772a7d47885e1","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打跑街定跑track?<br />\n<br />\n我成日跑左一次就放棄左<br />\n有冇辦法可以keep到團火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑街<br />\n當你成功減到肥唔想再肥返就會有恒心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未成功之前呢</blockquote><br />\n搵個目標比自己<br />\n如果你係想減肥既咪set一個月要減到幾多<br />\n之後未減到之前都要keep住跑+節食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果純粹想練既就set每2-3日一定要跑一次<br />\n幾夜都好唔好比籍口自己<br />\n當你換好衫落到街就自然有動力跑<br />\n係決定跑之前個心魔會叫你唔好跑姐"},{"pid":"c2fdd44d694b95ec2cd5a78bef08c6391647038b","tid":260521,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:25:53.000Z","msg":"行定跑？"},{"pid":"9a3d0ad4c0060c616c291835c4b479e2d94563a9","tid":260521,"uid":51578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:27:08.000Z","msg":"之前用runkeeper計跑極都係7分8分/km<br />\n<br />\n心諗點解練極都慢人咁多<br />\n<br />\n之後轉左runtastic 變番5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n到底係邊個準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907e05d01eaec67d689e65488917ffe82c628e98","tid":260521,"uid":91091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:32:40.000Z","msg":"樓主幾歲？近30?"},{"pid":"0188171f8e0e12c17a3472e042bfb620d1d83afa","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前用runkeeper計跑極都係7分8分/km<br />\n<br />\n心諗點解練極都慢人咁多<br />\n<br />\n之後轉左runtastic 變番5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n到底係邊個準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我買過apple watch發覺sync唔到條路線去iphone就無再用<br />\n所以講唔到你聽<br />\n不過咁大分別既 7變5喎"},{"pid":"bf376aadd06d851fbd639a8b8cc9cb24b6f15b3b","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主幾歲？近30?</blockquote><br />\n26(好似係"},{"pid":"3bdd58719c7981858b838065ec3b4cf24384ad06","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T08:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行定跑？</blockquote><br />\n跑啦緊係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行既效率低好多"},{"pid":"f205b37e8bdd8b7314747cc60331b9cbf1d55780","tid":260521,"uid":120092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:18:59.000Z","msg":"我每次做完gym都會跑跑步機<br />\n但成日跑幾分就橫隔膜痛<br />\n正確既呼吸方法係點?"},{"pid":"9798cecbd188edcdc12c056665d026b955237d8c","tid":260521,"uid":89928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:49:13.000Z","msg":"之前跑到7K<br />\n幾個月無跑，睇到樓主個po重燃我跑步欲望<br />\n但今朝跑得果4K已經捱唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9baf7214f799f2b2f06949963c706c894c5c74dd","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前跑到7K<br />\n幾個月無跑，睇到樓主個po重燃我跑步欲望<br />\n但今朝跑得果4K已經捱唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/131939_09e6275df710859ca2aa1842331c162b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F131939_09e6275df710859ca2aa1842331c162b.jpg&h=ac083b3f&s={SIZE}\" />加油呀 尋晚又跑左個半馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac3527dcfaccf2c4dceaef71fcca92cc5cf96fa","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我每次做完gym都會跑跑步機<br />\n但成日跑幾分就橫隔膜痛<br />\n正確既呼吸方法係點?</blockquote><br />\n跑步機唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我跑得急/耐都會橫隔膜痛<br />\n你試下跑慢啲"},{"pid":"a7e6216109ca7cdb31dc454611ae99783f98fbf4","tid":260521,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:22:02.000Z","msg":"點保護個KNEE?"},{"pid":"10cc42f9da7f6bbf7ebc17fc73c0715c04204a3c","tid":260521,"uid":89928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前跑到7K<br />\n幾個月無跑，睇到樓主個po重燃我跑步欲望<br />\n但今朝跑得果4K已經捱唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/131939_09e6275df710859ca2aa1842331c162b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F131939_09e6275df710859ca2aa1842331c162b.jpg&h=ac083b3f&s={SIZE}\" />加油呀 尋晚又跑左個半馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今朝勁曬辛苦程度直線上升，同尾冬初春果陣無得比<br />\n不過會堅持一星期跑三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望堅持到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a8c8c213310b32a24826e3e9dfc7b952ec68ae","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:31:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點保護個KNEE?</blockquote><br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以著壓力褲/護knee個啲可能長遠有幫助<br />\n不過暫時未出事無用過<br />\n行山先會"},{"pid":"e51ff8df8a2373ac04d3c3ce50f4ef6427a41a90","tid":260521,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前跑到7K<br />\n幾個月無跑，睇到樓主個po重燃我跑步欲望<br />\n但今朝跑得果4K已經捱唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/131939_09e6275df710859ca2aa1842331c162b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F131939_09e6275df710859ca2aa1842331c162b.jpg&h=ac083b3f&s={SIZE}\" />加油呀 尋晚又跑左個半馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今朝勁曬辛苦程度直線上升，同尾冬初春果陣無得比<br />\n不過會堅持一星期跑三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望堅持到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油<br />\n我試過太陽未落山同日出個時跑真係會辛苦好多<br />\n時間許可最好夜晚先跑又小人啲"},{"pid":"abf7f2eefc61bd220303e5c8ffd538d20e7f2611","tid":260521,"uid":3239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"平時會跑1k 就行兩三分鐘再跑<br />\n如果唔係一次過跑3-40分鐘隻腳會好攰<br />\n係咪正常？"},{"pid":"6edfabfd1329d3599d37b81c73c82ca3365ab938","tid":260521,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點保護個KNEE?</blockquote><br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以著壓力褲/護knee個啲可能長遠有幫助<br />\n不過暫時未出事無用過<br />\n行山先會</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我有踢開波,KNEE比較易痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62005fd1ce4869e41932999d41491f919265fcbf","tid":260521,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/133851_14175faa08bd9217d48e1764ca515fee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F133851_14175faa08bd9217d48e1764ca515fee.jpg&h=9bd2b753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右腳中左ITBS, 呢幾個月一跑頭幾k 就痛。試下一個月唔跑做 foam rolling 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c68f6cba5e3a3b614fbf71671e041689f01d9ea","tid":260521,"uid":120092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我每次做完gym都會跑跑步機<br />\n但成日跑幾分就橫隔膜痛<br />\n正確既呼吸方法係點?</blockquote><br />\n跑步機唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我跑得急/耐都會橫隔膜痛<br />\n你試下跑慢啲</blockquote><br />\n就算唔用跑步機<br />\n平時跑都有時痛<br />\n咁如果跑慢啲都痛既咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3433d64ed55d5f84f0ea891d0bd931bcec31e17","tid":260521,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我每次做完gym都會跑跑步機<br />\n但成日跑幾分就橫隔膜痛<br />\n正確既呼吸方法係點?</blockquote><br />\n跑步機唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我跑得急/耐都會橫隔膜痛<br />\n你試下跑慢啲</blockquote><br />\n就算唔用跑步機<br />\n平時跑都有時痛<br />\n咁如果跑慢啲都痛既咁點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我細個踢波果陣都會,好似係唔夠氣果陣就會咁,定還是有其他原因?而家已經唔會"},{"pid":"c9fca4ae6872b89cd47546dbbd609fa37c1597f7","tid":260521,"uid":4155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"睇撚錯一個月跑800km<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}